[Student "S"]
{This is a sign-off hand. If West hadn't bid you would either have bid 2\S, which partner would have passed, or 2\H, transferring partner to 2\S which YOU would have passed.

With lebensohl you can do the same thing, so you bid 2\S and partner passes.}

